{
  "text": "Could you tell us its mechanism? I am Ra. The Orion group cannot interfere directly but only through pre-existing distortions of mind/body/spirit complexes. Thus in this case, this entity reached for an heavy object with one hand and this miscalculated action caused a deformation or distortion of the skeletal/muscular structure of one of this instrument's appendages. Your aid may be helpful in supporting this instrument in the proper care of this distortion which is equivalent to what you call your post-operative state when bones are not firmly knit. This instrument needs to be aware of care necessary to avoid such miscalculated actions and your support in this state of awareness is noted and encouraged.",
